headline: DEWALT Encourages High School Seniors Attending Trade School to Celebrate Their Decision
summary: To honor and support the next generation of skilled tradespeople, DEWALT, a Stanley Black & Decker brand and leader in jobsite solutions, is recognizing high school seniors entering the trades starting on National Decision Day, traditionally held on May 1.
